CryptoProdCatgWalletGroup.name: CryptoProdCatgWalletGroup
CryptoProdCatgWalletGroup.description: Specifies if CryptoWalletGroup is in the allowlist or airdrop for the ProductCategory. A custom object between ProductCategory and CryptoWalletGroup adding the CryptoWalletGroup to allowlist or airdrop.

Status.description: Specifies if CryptoProdCatgWalletGroup is active and functional, or inactive and disabled.

Type.description: Determines whether the list of wallets is for minting allowlist or for executing an airdrop.
